    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>游戏介绍：</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎体验<strong>《TUST奇缘》</strong>——一款温馨动人的视觉小说游戏，带你重返青涩的大学时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从踏入校门的那一刻起，你将开启一段充满梦想与挑战的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将邂逅心仪的对象，编织属于你们的甜蜜恋曲；与室友共度欢笑与泪水，收获珍贵的友情；在忙碌与成长中，感受来自父母的深切关怀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个选择都影响着你的人生轨迹，每一次经历都将成为难忘的回忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《TUST奇缘》</strong>，让你的大学生活不再只是幻想，而是触手可及的美好。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>人物介绍：</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras/0464ad52b23fd3a8e060137da7bf7ce8.avif?t=1760800246\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras_big/0464ad52b23fd3a8e060137da7bf7ce8.avif?t=1760800246 width=800 height=448 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras/b05e1717929a9bc9af1d20145759bf32.avif?t=1760800246\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras_big/b05e1717929a9bc9af1d20145759bf32.avif?t=1760800246 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras/0285e4fa9b7fc228ae682bb010fc49ed.avif?t=1760800246\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras_big/0285e4fa9b7fc228ae682bb010fc49ed.avif?t=1760800246 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras/982aa6d98930df815f9aa53e428d29bc.avif?t=1760800246\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras_big/982aa6d98930df815f9aa53e428d29bc.avif?t=1760800246 width=800 height=452 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras/e034861befc562d05decc1ffd25073d7.avif?t=1760800246\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324270/extras_big/e034861befc562d05decc1ffd25073d7.avif?t=1760800246 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>作者介绍：</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >围观贤士sjy</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在校大学生</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >业余音乐人</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创业三年半</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此人负责此游戏的编剧、程序、背景、音乐。总体来说就是全权负责，一人独立制作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>特别致谢：</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >围观贤士的音源店</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天津市和平区弦事软件销售店</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天津市弦事音乐有限责任公司</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
